5:22:10.000Z","msg":"佢跳樓死撚咗未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6becb1939533d43a3688ae7f9fdd740d7fc5c16","tid":2059363,"uid":263297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"我唔係香港做野，公司有幾個大陸同事，都係後生嘅，2x-3x<br />\n本來以為係外國10年8年佢地會自動認清中共嘅咀臉，我真係太天真<br />\n一聽到我地講大陸點點點 就話我地班香港人比人呃 fake news 話美國搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係個group到一講武漢肺炎d數係假，即刻起哂鋼護主<br />\n剩係睇大陸放出黎嘅新聞，到而家佢地真係信到十足十 肺炎係美國搞出黎<br />\n又話陳同佳已經去左自首，我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係同個post嘅小粉紅一9樣"},{"pid":"b5d96831db57c4af9e5302933dfc140f71aa8fe6","tid":2059363,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3286cc0bb836dd1e68c5ba3bfe1ecd288f53b6","tid":2059363,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"大半個月的舊聞啦, 不過每次睇都倍兒爽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:48:37.000Z","msg":"之前係唔係有巴打post過?"}]}